Webkit version 0.01
===================

This is a Perl interface to QtWebkit.
It supports wkhtmltopdf patched fork of Qt which allows running this module without X server.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
 * Qt 4 with development headers, built with support of QtNetwork and QtWebkit

